===Pronunciation===
*πνευματικός / pneumatikos / phyoo-mat-ik-os'
*From G4151; non-carnal, that is, (humanly) ethereal (as opposed to gross), or (daemoniacally) a spirit (concretely), or (divinely) supernatural, regenerate, religious: 
